<HEADLINE>
NATO COVER-UP OF KOSOVO'S URANIUM POISONING EXPOSED  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Second of 8-part series, `My Return to Kosovo's Killing Fields')   (This provocative 750-word ``separate-buy'' article _ second of an
eight-part special report by Robert Fisk, ``My Return to Kosovo's
Killing Fields'' _ is from THE INDEPENDENT newspaper in London.)  
  
