<HEADLINE>
KOSOVO'S RELIGIOUS DESECRATION IS NATO'S SHAME  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Third of 8-part series, `My Return to Kosovo's Killing Fields')   (This provocative 825-word (trimmed) ``separate-buy'' article _
third of an eight-part special report by Robert Fisk, ``My Return
to Kosovo's Killing Fields'' _ is from THE INDEPENDENT newspaper in
London.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
in Canada EXCEPT to The Hamilton (Ontario) Spectator.)  
  
