NYT-01-03-00 1732EST &QL; 
</TRAILER>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT20000103.0244 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-03 17:33 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5532 &Cx1f; tad-z
u p BC-CAMPAIGN04-COX     01-03 1023
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CAMPAIGN04-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    ATTENTION, BORED VOTERS: PRESIDENTIAL RACES ENTERING KEY PHASE
 &HT;    With CAMPAIGN-TIMELINE. Moving in (w) Washington and (p)
politics categories.
 &HT;    By SCOTT SHEPARD
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
