u v BC-GRAPHIC-FILES-NYT &LR;      01-03 0126
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GRAPHIC-FILES-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here is a listing of the New York Times News Service Macintosh
graphics files that moved Monday, 010300. Included is the
