   ALL BUDGETED STORIES HAVE MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   Recapping: the story GORE-BRADLEY supercedes the separate GORE
and BRADLEY stories scheduled earlier.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y. Times News Service.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-01-03-00 2213EST &QL; 
</TRAILER>
